      public Camp(String campID, String campName, Faculty faculty, String location, String description, LocalDate campStartDate, LocalDate campEndDate, LocalDate regCloseDate, int totalSlots, int committeeSlots, boolean visibility, Staff staff)
      Constructs a new camp with the provided information, used to generate from csv
      Parameters:
      campID - unique id for camp.
      campName - camp name
      faculty - faculty camp is under
      location - camp location
      description - camp description
      campStartDate - start date of the camp.
      campEndDate - end date of the camp.
      regCloseDate - registration close date for the camp.
      totalSlots - total number of slots available
      committeeSlots - maximum number of committee slots available
      visibility - camp visibility status
      staff - staff member that created the camp
